      <title>美国称俄罗斯与朝鲜的武器贸易违反制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/us-says-russia-s-arms-trade-with-north-korea-violates-sanctions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国驻联合国大使表示，俄罗斯与朝鲜的武器贸易违反了国际制裁，在莫斯科否决了一项维持监测小组的措施后，华盛顿将寻求方法来监视违规行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/us-says-russia-s-arms-trade-with-north-korea-violates-sanctions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 02:53:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚计划增加 320 亿美元国防开支以应对新威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/australia-plans-32-billion-defense-boost-to-face-new-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚承诺在未来十年内将其军事开支增加 503 亿澳元（合 320 亿美元），国防部长理查德·马勒斯警告该国面临着二战以来“最复杂的战略环境”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/australia-plans-32-billion-defense-boost-to-face-new-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 02:32:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪利用表情包、音乐和自拍照来吸引印度的年轻选民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/india-elections-2024-modi-uses-memes-music-and-selfies-to-woo-young-voters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一对明显焦急的夫妇在机场外等待女儿的到来。经过看似痛苦的等待后，女孩跑出机场，对父母说：“无论情况如何，我都告诉过你们，莫迪先生会带我们回家。”]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/india-elections-2024-modi-uses-memes-music-and-selfies-to-woo-young-voters</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大企业称加税可能导致生产力进一步下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/canadian-businesses-say-tax-hike-risks-deeper-productivity-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大提高资本利得税的决定受到企业的批评，他们警告此举只会加剧该国的投资和生产力困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/canadian-businesses-say-tax-hike-risks-deeper-productivity-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 00:30:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>道明·考恩 (TD Cowen) 表示，在美上市的中国公司面临更高的退市风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/us-traded-china-firms-face-higher-delisting-risk-td-cowen-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[TD Cowen 表示，美国国会可能会迫使该国证券交易所将一些中国公司退市，这是一个“真实且不断上升的风险”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/us-traded-china-firms-face-higher-delisting-risk-td-cowen-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 00:16:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚将于 2024 年推进期待已久的补贴削减</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/malaysia-to-push-ahead-with-long-awaited-subsidy-cuts-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚经济部长表示，为了缩小财政赤字，马来西亚今年将削减汽油补贴。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/malaysia-to-push-ahead-with-long-awaited-subsidy-cuts-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍勃·梅南德斯准备在贿赂案辩护中指责他的妻子</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/bob-menendez-poised-to-blame-his-wife-in-bribery-case-defense</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份新公布的法庭文件显示，美国参议员鲍勃·梅嫩德斯准备在受贿案审判中指责他的妻子向他隐瞒了有关他们据称从寻求好处的商人那里收受礼物的信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/bob-menendez-poised-to-blame-his-wife-in-bribery-case-defense</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 23:42:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国将在袭击以色列后制裁伊朗无人机计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/us-to-sanction-iranian-drone-program-after-attack-on-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗周末袭击以色列，威胁将中东推入更广泛的冲突，美国将对伊朗实施新的制裁，目标是该国的导弹和无人机计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/us-to-sanction-iranian-drone-program-after-attack-on-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 23:10:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰总理表示财政紧缩是抑制物价、刺激经济增长的关键</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/nz-pm-says-fiscal-restraint-key-to-taming-prices-stoking-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰总理克里斯托弗·卢克森(Christopher Luxon)在发布其政府第一份财政蓝图前几周表示，新西兰需要检查政府支出，以成功抑制通货膨胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/nz-pm-says-fiscal-restraint-key-to-taming-prices-stoking-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 09:35:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
